<br>
for example<br>
<br>
3rd level paladin weapon cap 3(+1) * 5 = 20<br>
3rd level warrior weapon cap 3(+1) * 5 = 20<br>
3rd level cleric weapon cap 3(+1) *4 = 16<br>
3rd level wizard weapon cap 3 (+1) * 3 = 12<br>
3rd level beastlord weapon cap 3 * 4 = 12<br>
<br>
I used my hand to hand up to skill level 10 and then went to train it and I could only put two points in.  This was at 3rd level.<br>
<br>
It seems like they will be pretty helpless in situations where they can't use their pets.  Kind of early to make those kind of statements, but that is my early impression.<br>
<br>
Oh yeah....it was rumored that they will have a weight limit (like the monk) but no one has reported seeing that in action as of yet.  If it is in, it doesn't seem to kick in at the early levels.<br>
<br>
